Titolo: Bomberman Hero

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Bomberman Hero (ボンバーマンヒーロー　～ミリアン王女 (おうじょ)を救 (すく)え!～, Bonbāman Hīrō ~Mirian-Ōjo o Sukue!~, Bomberman Hero: Rescue Princess Millian!) is a platforming video game and the second Bomberman game for the Nintendo 64.  Bomberman Hero is more advanced in terms of gameplay, as well as having more levels, bosses, weapons, and character moves. However, it lacks multiplayer and therefore focuses on the single player action. This game was available on the Wii Virtual Console service.

Genere: Platforming 

Valutazione: N/A
